00:30:30.925 --> 00:30:32.300
TIA KANSARA HON
FRIBA: Thank you.

00:30:32.300 --> 00:30:34.820
AUDIENCE: My question
is around this.

00:30:34.820 --> 00:30:37.240
I find this is a
fascinating new challenge.

00:30:37.240 --> 00:30:40.850
Because from one side,
our actions as individuals

00:30:40.850 --> 00:30:45.160
can individually impact
negatively Planet Earth.

00:30:45.160 --> 00:30:49.200
But we don't reap the benefit
unless we act collectively,

00:30:49.200 --> 00:30:52.840
either at the local level or
at the country level, or even

00:30:52.840 --> 00:30:54.440
at the Earth level.

00:30:54.440 --> 00:30:57.330
Which makes our action
remote, or the impact

00:30:57.330 --> 00:31:00.384
remote from the action
that we do as individuals.

00:31:00.384 --> 00:31:06.170
And breaking this vicious
cycle of us doing good actions

00:31:06.170 --> 00:31:09.332
and seeing the benefit
is very critical.

00:31:09.332 --> 00:31:11.444
Now there are a lot
of government actions,

00:31:11.444 --> 00:31:13.790
from a regulation point of
view which have been around,

00:31:13.790 --> 00:31:18.540
effective or not, subject
to politics and economics,

00:31:18.540 --> 00:31:24.140
and technology clearly has
some efficiency promise

00:31:24.140 --> 00:31:25.211
for companies.

00:31:25.211 --> 00:31:27.416
But I love what you
mentioned about bringing it

00:31:27.416 --> 00:31:29.700
to an individual
level, and having

00:31:29.700 --> 00:31:34.690
the index on every bottle
or on every product.

00:31:34.690 --> 00:31:37.370
So my question for
you is that when

00:31:37.370 --> 00:31:41.090
we see a calorie or
an organic label,

00:31:41.090 --> 00:31:43.928
we link that to ourselves or
our individual [INAUDIBLE]..

00:31:43.928 --> 00:31:46.790
But when we see a
replenish label,

00:31:46.790 --> 00:31:51.130
we cannot relate it to
our individual well-being,

00:31:51.130 --> 00:31:54.080
unless everyone
else sign up for it.

00:31:54.080 --> 00:31:57.835
How do you think are the most
interesting ideas and the most

00:31:57.835 --> 00:32:02.482
effective ones in relating more
of this index or similar labels

00:32:02.482 --> 00:32:06.350
to individual well-being,
being tangible or nontangible?

00:32:06.350 --> 00:32:09.200
TIA KANSARA HON FRIBA: That's
such an interesting way

